= sfDoctrineActAsKeyValueStorePlugin =

== What It's For ==

sfDoctrineActAsKeyValueStorePlugin is a Doctrine behavior that lets you
store additional attribute values along with any Doctrine object without 
the need for a schema change. 

For more information please see 
[http://trac.apostrophenow.org/wiki/sfDoctrineActAsKeyValueStorePlugin the Apostrophe Wiki] where 
this plugin is documented in detail. You do not have to use Apostrophe to use this plugin.
